Setting up a style sheet
    - add the following in header to link to a style sheet:
        - <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/styles.css">
    - otherwise, you can add it in <head> directly using <style> </style>

Loading client-side javascript file
    - use a script tag 
        - <script src="./js/app.js"></script>

Loading images
    - use a img tag 
        - <img src="data/img/macbook-pro-15.jpg" alt="" class="laptop__img">

********** NOTE ********** 
    - all paths are relative to "public" folder